import React from 'react'
import {ChakraProvider, Container, Box, Stack, Flex } from '@chakra-ui/react';

const Section3 = () => {
    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Container maxW="1364px" h="1000px" bg="blue.500">
                <Stack direction="column" mt="100px">
                    <Box>
                        <Flex justify='center'>
                            <Stack direction="column" spacing="30px">
                                <Box w="264px" h="53px"  bg="tomato">
                                    
                                </Box>
                                <Box w="674px" h="169px"  bg="tomato">
                                    
                                </Box>
                                <Box w="260px" h="48px"  bg="tomato">
                                    
                                </Box>
                            </Stack>
                        </Flex>
                    </Box>
                    <Box>
                        <Box w="1364" h="231px"  bg="white">
                            1
                        </Box>
                    </Box>
                </Stack>
            </Container>
        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}

export default Section3
